4.65/5  rDev +4%look: 4.25 | smell: 4.75 | taste: 4.75 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.5Pours brownish black with a bubbly head that disappates quickly without leaving any lacing.  The smell is tons of chocolate and coffee with little, if any, barrel. The taste is pretty similar to Pirate Bomb!.  For some reason, barreling Bomb! seems to simply enhance the already amazing flavors.  Not because of the whiskey flavor, but because it seems to act like salt; a flavor enhancer.  I wish the flavor was more obvious. but because of everything that goes into the base beer, it would be tough to impart a forward whiskey flavor.  
