Mouthful is medium and smooth with low carbonation.  Finish lingers and is a touch warming.
A very solid stout.  More reminiscent of a sweet stout than a imperial stout.  The biggest drawback (for me) was the mouthful - I felt it could be heartier.  All other aspects were very solid especially if you prefer sweeter stouts.  I would definitely give this a try against the original. 587 charactersSlack, Jun 11, 2016
